{"tid":15810,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[lihkg有愛]聖誕節送水餃","createTime":"2016-12-01T07:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T18:44:57.000Z","uid":24165,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77f25d0f2fc043b20aa4137ac436abc32097f562","tid":15810,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說早排係facebook見到呢個post話送水餃<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/142601_d0587eb40858521a6adae13dd863c9c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F142601_d0587eb40858521a6adae13dd863c9c0.jpg&h=e19ac26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就禁幾個制試下 琴日就去左尖沙咀分店拎 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/144601_0298e69ac17a6d238a1380972ceafc6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F144601_0298e69ac17a6d238a1380972ceafc6c.jpg&h=8122c366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都幾大包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且都幾易拎<br />\n只係要個電話no. 拎又唔洗對身份<br />\n名同email可以亂填<br />\n之後會收到sms話係個期限內去分店攞<br />\n<br />\n之後我忽發奇想 可唔可以收集到幾十包水餃係聖誕派比露宿者etc? <br />\n基本上零成本 除左容器餐具個啲<br />\n所以我想請各位巴絲打用小小時間登記<br />\n收到sms之後forward比我去拎水餃<br />\n（只需要個msg 我唔會知你電話no. ）<br />\n我煮完就拎去派 大家覺得可唔可行? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"http://www.wcfgreenday.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wcfgreenday.com%2F&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ad956573\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wcfgreenday.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw 就算你地認為唔可行都可以去拎返一兩包返屋企煮 我覺得都幾好食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c48efdffc30407e43b40d15c18700f3109ffe9e","tid":15810,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb06eb1875cc85de74dc872eab0051bb1466866","tid":15810,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9b26237b0d0e9f0ff777313881799ba7cd44f7b5","tid":15810,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"巴打有愛 定我返到香港幫幫你<br />\n人在日本"},{"pid":"2066b7d623928be17612179a2572348760cd374d","tid":15810,"uid":46920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"試試佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9070e6cf6c357b33da7f2c3a1c22bc146b6ac95","tid":15810,"uid":47790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"留個名先 又諗少餐食乜 thanks"},{"pid":"18595e408a8e4ca69a5eea754d2b90f7b69d2087","tid":15810,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"露宿者點煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹好奇<br />\n定煮埋拎比佢地好"},{"pid":"d5a2711e4277e937035daae108f0dd14b37403c4","tid":15810,"uid":24526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:54:28.000Z","msg":"我揀果陣得中環店 無尖咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b962ee70d9ab7f8be9a886cb515987fda90ecd33","tid":15810,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有愛 定我返到香港幫幫你<br />\n人在日本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c23adfcae6941c086041df1df23069809e3545","tid":15810,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"岩岩開左個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">telegram: lihkg3pigs</span><br />\n<br />\n唔得閒去拎又想幫人既巴絲可以forward個sms比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\